#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.155"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.155:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.155:0.2"
msgid "16. Saddhammavagga"
msgstr "16. The True Teaching"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.155:0.3"
msgid "155. Dutiyasaddhammasammosasutta"
msgstr "155. The Decline of the True Teaching (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.155:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcime, bhikkhave, dhammā saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, these five things lead to the decline and disappearance of the "
"true teaching."

msgctxt "an5.155:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.155:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhū dhammaṃ na pariyāpuṇanti—"
msgstr "It’s when the mendicants don’t memorize the teaching—"

msgctxt "an5.155:1.4"
msgid ""
"suttaṃ, geyyaṃ, veyyākaraṇaṃ, gāthaṃ, udānaṃ, itivuttakaṃ, jātakaṃ, "
"abbhutadhammaṃ, vedallaṃ."
msgstr ""
"statements, songs, discussions, verses, inspired sayings, legends, stories "
"of past lives, amazing stories, and analyses."

msgctxt "an5.155:1.5"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo dhammo saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya "
"saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"This is the first thing that leads to the decline and disappearance of the "
"true teaching."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.155:2.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ na "
"vitthārena paresaṃ desenti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, the mendicants don’t explain the teaching in detail to others "
"as they learned and memorized it."

msgctxt "an5.155:2.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo dhammo saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya "
"saṃvattati."
msgstr "This is the second thing …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: paraṃ → paresaṃ (bj, s1, km, pts1) | pare (?)
msgctxt "an5.155:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ na "
"vitthārena paraṃ vācenti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, the mendicants don’t make others recite the teaching in detail "
"as they learned and memorized it."

msgctxt "an5.155:3.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo dhammo saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya "
"saṃvattati."
msgstr "This is the third thing …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.155:4.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ na "
"vitthārena sajjhāyaṃ karonti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, the mendicants don’t recite the teaching in detail as they "
"learned and memorized it."

msgctxt "an5.155:4.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho dhammo saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya "
"saṃvattati."
msgstr "This is the fourth thing …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.155:5.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ na "
"cetasā anuvitakkenti anuvicārenti manasānupekkhanti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, the mendicants don’t think about and consider the teaching in "
"their hearts, examining it with their minds as they learned and memorized it."

msgctxt "an5.155:5.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamo dhammo saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya "
"saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"This is the fifth thing that leads to the decline and disappearance of the "
"true teaching."

msgctxt "an5.155:5.3"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca dhammā saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya "
"saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"These five things lead to the decline and disappearance of the true teaching."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.178"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.155:6.1"
msgid ""
"Pañcime, bhikkhave, dhammā saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya anantaradhānāya "
"saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"These five things lead to the continuation, persistence, and enduring of the "
"true teaching."

msgctxt "an5.155:6.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.155:6.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhū dhammaṃ pariyāpuṇanti—"
msgstr "It’s when the mendicants memorize the teaching—"

msgctxt "an5.155:6.4"
msgid ""
"suttaṃ, geyyaṃ, veyyākaraṇaṃ, gāthaṃ, udānaṃ, itivuttakaṃ, jātakaṃ, "
"abbhutadhammaṃ, vedallaṃ."
msgstr ""
"statements, songs, discussions, verses, inspired sayings, legends, stories "
"of past lives, amazing stories, and analyses."

msgctxt "an5.155:6.5"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo dhammo saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya "
"anantaradhānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"This is the first thing that leads to the continuation, persistence, and "
"enduring of the true teaching."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an5.155:7.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ "
"vitthārena paresaṃ desenti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, the mendicants explain the teaching in detail to others as they "
"learned and memorized it."

msgctxt "an5.155:7.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo dhammo saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya "
"anantaradhānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr "This is the second thing …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an5.155:8.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ "
"vitthārena paraṃ vācenti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, the mendicants make others recite the teaching in detail as "
"they learned and memorized it."

msgctxt "an5.155:8.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo dhammo saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya "
"anantaradhānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr "This is the third thing …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an5.155:9.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ "
"vitthārena sajjhāyaṃ karonti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, the mendicants recite the teaching in detail as they learned "
"and memorized it."

msgctxt "an5.155:9.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho dhammo saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya "
"anantaradhānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr "This is the fourth thing …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an5.155:10.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ cetasā "
"anuvitakkenti anuvicārenti manasānupekkhanti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, the mendicants think about and consider the teaching in their "
"hearts, examining it with their minds as they learned and memorized it."

msgctxt "an5.155:10.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamo dhammo saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya "
"anantaradhānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"This is the fifth thing that leads to the continuation, persistence, and "
"enduring of the true teaching."

msgctxt "an5.155:10.3"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca dhammā saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya "
"anantaradhānāya saṃvattantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"These five things lead to the continuation, persistence, and enduring of the "
"true teaching.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.155:10.4"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
